.TH DCR-CLEAN 1 "2026-06-02" "dcr 0.7.0" "DCR Manual"
.SH NAME
dcr-clean \- Remove build artifacts
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B dcr clean
[\fB\-\-debug\fR | \fB\-\-release\fR]
[\fB\-\-target\fR \fI<triple>\fR]
[\fB\-\-all\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Removes build artifacts from the target directory.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-debug
Clean debug artifacts (default).
.TP
.B \-\-release
Clean release artifacts.
.TP
.B \-\-target \fI<triple>\fR
Clean artifacts for a specific target.
.TP
.B \-\-all
Clean all workspace members.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR dcr (1),
.BR dcr-build (1)
